      p.fab.fa-artstation(aria-hidden='true')       Working at the intersection of content delivery, application development and information security. 
    div.bullet2
      p.fas.fa-cloud-upload-alt(aria-hidden='true')      Delivering platforms to enable commerce and deliver secure transaction platforms for consumers and merchants alike.
    div.bullet3
      p.fab.fa-accusoft(aria-hidden='true')      Harnessing cutting edge technologies with a philosophy of open-source and freely-distributed. 
    div.bullet4
      p.fab.fa-battle-net(aria-hidden='true')      Java makes the world go round, and cloud development will always have a place for nascient systems. 
    div.topcontainercontent2
      |
      div.fab.fa-github(aria-hidden='true')    Github:
